Эта вики посвящена серии игр Dark Souls в жанре action/RPG. Серия разработанная компанией From Software, являет собой духовного наследника игры Demon's Souls.

Основной особенностью игры является уникальная сложность, созданная благодаря спектру особенностей: враждебный игроку мир, пропитанный отчаянием и наполненный чудовищами всех мастей и размеров, уникальная подача сюжета, понимание которого зависит от воображения и желания самого игрока, гибкая система улучшения персонажа и снаряжения, позволяющая создать героя "под себя" и особая онлайн-система, прочно вплетенная в геймплей. 

Ваша судьба будет зависеть от умения правильно оценивать ситуацию и выстраивать стратегию поведения, быстро обучаться и быть непредсказуемым. Dark Souls потребует от вас абсолютной концентрации и будет сурово наказывать за ошибки. Однако умирая вы будете становиться сильнее.

items.name: Warhammer 40k
items.title: Warhammer 40k
items.headline: Warhammer 40,000 Wiki
items.desc:
"It is the 41st Millennium. For more than a hundred centuries the Emperor of Mankind has sat immobile on the Golden Throne of Earth. He is the master of mankind by the will of the gods and master of a million worlds by the might of his inexhaustible armies. He is a rotting carcass writhing invisibly with power from the Dark Age of Technology. He is the Carrion Lord of the vast Imperium of Man for whom a thousand souls are sacrificed every day so that he may never truly die.Yet even in his deathless state, the Emperor continues his eternal vigilance. Mighty battlefleets cross the daemon-infested miasma of the Warp, the only route between distant stars, their way lit by the Astronomican, the psychic manifestation of the Emperor's will. Vast armies give battle in His name on uncounted worlds. Greatest amongst his soldiers are the Adeptus Astartes, the Space Marines, bio-engineered super-warriors. Their comrades in arms are legion: the Imperial Guard and countless planetary defence forces, the ever-vigilant Inquisition and the tech-priests of the Adeptus Mechanicus to name only a few. But for all their multitudes, they are barely enough to hold off the ever-present threat to humanity from aliens, heretics, mutants -- and far, far worse. To be a man in such times is to be one amongst untold billions. It is to live in the cruelest and most bloody regime imaginable. These are the tales of those times. Forget the power of technology and science, for so much has been forgotten, never to be relearned. Forget the promise of progress and understanding, for in the grim dark future there is only war. There is no peace amongst the stars, only an eternity of carnage and slaughter, and the laughter of thirsting gods." 

Warhammer 40k Wiki is a collaborative project to create the most definitive and accurate reference for everything related to the Warhammer 40,000 universe.

items.name: Baldur's Gate Wiki
items.title: Baldur's Gate Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Baldur's Gate wiki!
items.desc:
The Baldur's Gate wiki strives to be the most accurate and complete source of information about the video games serie it covers and we try to build a helpful and friendly community. The games are set in the Forgotten Realms. The wiki has more than 2,000 pages of content and more than 2500 photos!

The two series of games of this wiki are:
 
The Bhaalspawn serie, based on the Infinity Engine developed by Bioware, is an isometric 2D western computer RPG which was started by the release of Baldur's Gate in 1998, which is considered as one of the best RPG's by many, even  until this very day. This also includes the expansion pack, Tales of the Sword Coast, which brought some major improvements and added more areas to explore.
 
The second game of this serie is Baldur's Gate II: Shadows of Amn, which continues after the events of Baldur's Gate, with Jon Irenicus as the main antagonist. This games has a major expansion pack, Throne of Bhaal, which brings closure to the serie.

We also cover Baldur's Gate: Enhanced Edition and  Baldur's Gate II: Enhanced Edition.

The second serie is the Dark Alliance Serie, with Baldur's Gate: Dark Alliance I and  Baldur's Gate: Dark Alliance II, which an action orientated serie which was released for the PS2 and the Xbox, but not for the pc.


Until then at the Baldur's Gate wiki!

items.name: Monster Girl Encyclopedia Wiki
items.title: Monster Girl Encyclopedia Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Monster Girl Encyclopedia Wiki
items.desc:
The Monster Girl Encyclopedia (MGE) is a compendium of knowledge concerning Monster Girls (MG) or Mamono, created by the artist Kenkou Cross. It is written from the viewpoint of a nameless traveler within the setting, who is going around the world documenting all known species and variants of Mamono. Since its inception, MGE has grown to include a larger setting, which paints a picture of a strained conflict between the Demon Lord and her Mamono, versus the Chief Goddess and her Order.

Currently, the MGE itself even has a place in the setting, as a secret published document that was written by a special task force, which is stationed at the palace of an unnamed anti-monster monarchy.

items.name: RuPaul's Drag Race Wiki
items.title: RuPaul's Drag Race Wiki
items.headline: RuPaul's Drag Race Wiki
items.desc:
'RuPaul's Drag Race' is a reality competition series produced by World of Wonder for the Logo Network, and is the subject of this wiki. Drag superstar RuPaul is the host, mentor and inspiration for this series, which details RuPaul's search for "America's next drag superstar."

The show was marked as the most watched series on Logo in its first season, and it became the most streamed series ever on LogoTV.com during its second. The title of the show is a play on drag queen and drag racing, with the title sequence and theme song "Drag Race" both having a drag racing theme.

items.name: Criminal Minds Wiki
items.title: Criminal Minds Wiki
items.headline: CRIMINAL MINDS WIKI... "To catch a criminal you have to think like one"
items.desc:
CRIMINAL MINDS WIKI is a collaborative encyclopedia for everything related to the CBS series.

CRIMINAL MINDS is an American police procedural drama that differs from many procedural dramas by focusing on the victims and the criminal rather than the crime itself.

CRIMINAL MINDS revolves around an elite team of profilers from the FBI's Behavioral Analysis Unit (BAU) at Quantico, Virginia. Profilers analyze the country's most twisted criminal minds in an effort to anticipate their next moves before they strike again. Each team member brings his or her own area of expertise to the table as they pinpoint predators' motivations and identify their emotional triggers in the attempt to stop them.

CRIMINAL MINDS WIKI offers you information about the show characters (main, secondary and one-timers), episodes (with their plots, quotes, references and music) and actors (main, recurring and guests). This WIKI offers you too information about the real life criminals that inspire all its life-a-like scripts, and the FBI agents (and other LEOs) that worked to stop them.

Over the course of a typical adventure, groups will have a blast fortifying locations, scavenging for supplies, trying to live off the land and negotiating with other people. The game is being developed entirely with the community in focus, and tons of features are based entirely on feedback.

items.name: High School DxD Wiki

items.desc:

The series revolves around Issei Hyoudou, a perverted high school student who is reincarnated into a Devil by Rias Gremory after being killed on his first date. He later joins the Occult Research Club as he strives to rise up the Devils' ranks to fulfill his dream of building a harem and becoming a "Harem King".

items.desc: All things about the outlaw biker club SAMCRO! The Sons of Anarchy Motorcycle Club Redwood Original (SAMCRO), also known as the Reaper Crew, is a outlaw motorcycle club based on the west coast of the United States. The club was formed by John Teller and Piney Winston, two Vietnam War veterans, in 1967 in Charming, California. It is commonly mistaken that the Sons Of Anarchy are based upon the Hells Angels, one of the largest motorcycle clubs in the real world. This cannot be true because in the 4th season it is said by Lincoln Potter that the Sons Of Anarchy are barely in the top 10 motorcycle clubs in the US. Welcome to Charming!

items.headline: Survivor Wiki is one of the best designed wikis in Wikia!
items.desc: Survivor Wiki is dedicated to the long-running reality show Survivor. Survivor is an American version of the Survivor reality television game show, itself derived from the Swedish television series Expedition Robinson originally created in 1997 by Charlie Parsons. The series premiered on May 31, 2000 on CBS. Now the 25th season Survivor: Philippines will premeire September 19th, 2012. It is one of the best designed wikis in Wikia!

items.name: Brickipedia
items.title: Brickipedia
items.headline: Brickipedia, the LEGO wiki
items.desc: Brickipedia is a popular, well-known website, consisting of over 32k pages and counting, with users who strive to show off their knowledge for LEGO. Brickipedia, located at lego.wikia.com, is Wikia's largest LEGO Wiki, which was founded on March 4, 2005. Brickipedia's goal is to provide a free online Encyclopedia on everything LEGO. Twelve years after it was established, Brickipedia has reached a size of over 30,000 articles, and has a few hundred active users right now. Join the community and share your love of LEGO today.

items.name: Xenopedia
items.title: Xenopedia
items.headline: Xenopedia - The Alien vs. Predator Wiki
items.desc: Xenopedia is a wiki-based database that anyone can edit containing detailed information on all characters, species, weapons, vehicles, etc. featured in the Alien, Predator and Alien vs. Predator films, games, books and comics. Founded in 2006, Xenopedia currently has over 2,000 articles, covering the Xenomorph, Yautja and everything in between.

items.name: Age of Empires Series Wiki
items.title: Age of Empires Series Wiki
items.headline: Age of Empires Wiki
items.desc: Age of Empires Wiki is about the "Age of Empires Series", the history-based, original real time strategy games of Ensemble Studios published by Microsoft Game Studios. The wiki has information about all of the Age of Empire series as well as its spin-offs, Age of Mythology.

items.name: Gossip Girl Wiki
items.title: Gossip Girl Wiki
items.headline: Check out the Gossip Girl Wiki
items.desc: Gossip Girl Wiki is a fanbase for the Gossip Girl books, the spin-off the It Girl novels, and popular CW series of the same name.  The wiki provides information on various romantic pairings, popularly known as "ships," of the Upper East Side world of Gossip Girl, as well as the latest scandals, frenemies, theories and gossip about the characters. If you're not already a part of the wiki, then you're missing out! Come join us now at the one and only Gossip Girl wiki, where you can socialize AND find out everything about GG.

items.name: Animal Crossing Wiki
items.title: Animal Crossing Wiki
items.headline: Animal Crossing Wiki
items.desc: The Animal Crossing Wiki is a collaborative encyclopedia for everything related to the Animal Crossing series. There are 1,677 articles and growing since this wiki was founded in August 2005. The wiki format allows anyone to create or edit any article, so we can all work together to create a comprehensive database for the Animal Crossing series.

items.name: Law and Order
items.title: Law and Order
items.headline: Law and Order Wiki
items.desc: Law and Order Wiki is a collaborative database for the Law and Order universe. The wiki contains information about the original Law and Order series as well as its spin-offs: Law and Order: SVU, Criminal Intent, Trial by Jury, UK, Los Angeles, and other related media releases.

items.name: Narutopedia
items.title: Narutopedia
items.headline: Willkommen im Naruto-Wiki
items.desc: Die Narutopedia ist eine interaktive Enzyklopädie über Masashi Kishimotos Mangareihe Naruto und die darauf basierenden Animeserie, Filme, Specials und Spiele. Wir begleiten den jungen Naruto Uzumaki aus Konohagakure, der es sich zum Ziel gemacht hat, ein Hokage, der oberste Ninja seines Dorfes, zu werden.

items.name: Fullmetal Alchemist Wiki
items.title: Fullmetal Alchemist Wiki
items.headline: Fullmetal Alchemist Wiki
items.desc: Fullmetal Alchemist Wiki is a free reference website for everything related to the Fullmetal Alchemist franchise, including extensive information on the manga chapters, anime episodes, video games, movies, and more.

items.name: Terraria Wiki
items.title: Terraria Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Terraria Wiki
items.desc:
Welcome to the Terraria Wiki that anyone can edit!

Whether you're looking for information on monsters, items, weapons, NPCs, crafting recipes or even mods, if it exists in Terraria, you'll find it at the Terraria Wiki. 

While you're there, be sure to check out the many helpful videos, as well as the fan art collections.

items.name: The Amazing World of Gumball Wiki
items.title: The Amazing World of Gumball Wiki
items.headline: The Amazing World of Gumball Wiki!
items.desc:
The Amazing World of Gumball Wiki is a collaborative effort dedicated to The Amazing World of Gumball, a British-American TV series that is currently airing on Cartoon Networks worldwide. The wiki contains all kinds of information on the show, such as episode guides and transcripts, plot summaries, galleries, and character information. In addition, there are forums and a chat room available for fans who want to discuss the show! 

We also feature fun monthly polls! Voice your opinion on the main page!

items.name: Pretty Little Liars Wiki
items.title: Pretty Little Liars Wiki
items.headline: Pretty Little Liars Wiki
items.desc:
Set
in the fictional town of Rosewood, Pennsylvania, the series follows
the lives of four girls, Aria
Montgomery, Hanna
Marin, Emily
Fields,
and Spencer
Hastings,
whose clique falls apart after the disappearance of their
leader, Alison
DiLaurentis.
One year later, the estranged friends are reunited as they begin
receiving messages from a mysterious figure named "A", who
threatens to expose their deepest secrets, including ones they
thought only Alison knew. At first, they think it's Alison herself,
but after her body is found, the girls realize that someone else is
planning on ruining their perfect lives. Later in the series the
original A, Mona Vanderwaal becomes a target herself and part of the
infamous group known in Rosewood as The Liars.

items.name: Idea Wiki
items.title: Idea Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Idea Wiki
items.desc:
Ideas are more powerful than guns." -Josef Stalin
"There is nothing more powerful than an idea whose time has come." -Victor Hugo
"Ideas can change the world." -Idea Wiki
Donate ideas and help make others better. Ideas are donated to the public in hopes they will one day become a reality. Please remember that all your contributions can be used by others.

items.name: Kancolle Wiki
items.title: Kancolle Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Kancolle Wiki!
items.desc: Kantai Collection, also known as KanColle, is an online browser game in which one assumes the role of an admiral, assembles a fleet of kanmusu ('ship girls' based on World War II-era ships and submarines), & battles against fleets of unknown warships.  This wiki is a place to find English information about the game & tutorials on how to play even without knowledge of Japanese. Additionally, information regarding the expanded franchise may be found, including manga, anime, other games, music, & more.

items.name: Gotham Wiki
items.title: Gotham Wiki
items.headline: Before Batman, there was Gotham
items.desc: Long before Batman began his crusade to save Gotham, Detective Jim Gordon fought against the criminals and the corrupt to save his city in the hit FOX series Gotham. This community is dedicated to housing a useful and informative database for all subject matter related to the show. Our goal is to collaborate with other fans in order to build a reliable, accurate resource with as much detailed information about episodes, characters, and story elements as possible. All are welcome to join in and contribute here, so long as edits are constructive, discussions are positive, and both are relevant to this series.

items.name: Wings of Fire Wiki
items.title: Wings of Fire Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Wings of Fire Wiki!
items.desc: The seven dragon tribes of Pyrrhia are at war, and it is up to a group of five unlikely heroes to save the day. Guided by a mysterious prophecy, will the dragonets' friendship and unique abilities be enough to find a new queen and unite the tribes once again?

items.name: PAW Patrol Wiki
items.title: PAW Patrol Wiki
items.headline: Come Join the PAW Patrol Wiki!
items.desc: The PAW Patrol Wiki is a special place where you can learn all about the hit Nick Jr. series, PAW Patrol! We have pages featuring information on characters, episodes, toys, places, galleries, and a whole load of extras! We also have a fantastic set of administrators that work hard to keep the silly editors and trolls away. If you love cute cartoon puppies, PAW Patrol is the show to watch! And if you love to learn, PAW Patrol Wiki is the place to be. So come and visit today!  Ruff ruff!

items.name: Mining Simulator Wiki
items.title: Mining Simulator Wiki
items.desc: Mining Simulator is a ROBLOX game developed by Runway Rumble. Team up with your friends, or go on a solo mining expedition to discover rare gems and become rich!

items.name: Outlander Wiki
items.title: Outlander Wiki
items.headline: Explore the Outlander Wikia
items.desc: The OUTLANDER Wikia community is a community based fan site and a collaborative effort to document everything related to the Outlander book series by Diana Gabaldon and the STARZ television adaptation. We strive to have detailed information about all the episodes, characters, actors, and more. Please join us in helping make this a top site for OUTLANDER.

items.name: The Big Bang Theory Wiki
items.title: The Big Bang Theory Wiki
items.headline: The Big Bang Theory Wiki
items.desc: The Big Bang Theory Wiki is a site for fans of the popular CBS television series The Big Bang Theory. The show is primarily centered on characters living in Pasadena, California: scientists Leonard Hofstadter, Sheldon Cooper, Howard Wolowitz, Raj Koothrappali,  Bernadette Rostenkowski Amy Farrah Fowler and waitress Penny. The geekiness and intellect of the four guys and their girlfriends is contrasted for comic effect with Penny's social skills and common sense.

items.name: A Wheel of Time Wiki
items.title: A Wheel of Time Wiki
items.headline: The Wheel of Time Wiki
items.desc: The Wheel of Time Wiki is a comprehensive resource for the epic fantasy novel series, The Wheel of Time, by Robert Jordan. The wiki contains over 5,000 pages dedicated to the series, which currently spans thirteen books in print and another on the way, now penned by Brandon Sanderson. WOT Wiki features detailed information on the plot, subplots, characters, and the complicated world of The Wheel of Time.

items.name: Harry Potter Wiki
items.title: Harry Potter Wiki
items.headline: Benvenuti babbani nella Harry Potter Wiki
items.desc: La Harry Potter Wiki è un'enciclopedia libera sulla popolare serie creata da J. K. Rowling, i film e tutto ciò che parla del mondo fantastico di Hogwarts e dei suoi maghi. Scopri tutto quello che volevi sapere su Harry, Ron e Hermione. Non importa se sei un babbano o un mago esperto, sarai il benvenuto!

items.name: Once Upon a Time Wiki
items.title: Once Upon a Time Wiki
items.headline: Once Upon a Time Wiki
items.desc: The one and only stop for all things Once Upon a Time!

items.name: Animated Foot Scene Wiki
items.title: Animated Foot Scene Wiki
items.headline: Animated Foot Scene Wiki
items.desc: "AnimeFeet", the Animated Foot Scenes Wiki includes many graphical mediums. We focus on all types of characters with an encyclopedic scope, hoping to appeal to a wider audience. We strive to capture, collect and store the most interesting foot scenes available to the watchers of anime and cartoons, and to the readers of manga and comic books.

items.name: Memory Beta, non-canon Star Trek Wiki
items.title: Memory Beta, non-canon Star Trek Wiki
items.headline: Memory Beta
items.desc: Memory Beta is an encyclopedia of non-canonical Star Trek information, including novels, comic books, RPG sourcebooks, video games and any other licensed works. Read about culture, characters, technology, starships, and more.

items.name: Friends Central
items.title: Friends Central
items.headline: Welcome to the Friends Wiki!
items.desc: Friends Central is a collaborative encyclopedia for everything related to NBC's Friends and its spin-off Joey. The wiki format allows anyone to create or edit articles, so we can all work together to create a comprehensive database for fans. We are currently editing 1,222 articles since March 15th, 2006 and you can help!

items.name: Soulcalibur Wiki
items.title: Soulcalibur Wiki
items.headline: Soulcalibur Wiki
items.desc: Soulcalibur Wiki is a site based on the Soul series of fighting games developed by Namco. It has information on all of the aspects of each game, such as characters, various weapons, stages, secrets, and more.

items.name: How to Get Away with Murder Wiki
items.title: How to Get Away with Murder Wiki
items.headline: How to Get Away with Murder
items.desc: This wiki is about the about the hit ABC show, How to Get Away with Murder. It tells the story of Annalise Keating, a defence attorney who also teaches students at a university. She hires a select group of them to come and work at her firm and help with the cases she's challenged with. Along the way secrets are both made and discovered - and some ultimately lead to an unfortunate murder...which the students are forced to cover up using their knowledge gained from working with Annalise.

items.name: Roblox Super Power Training Simulator Wiki
items.title: Roblox Super Power Training Simulator Wiki

items.name: Metal Gear Wiki
items.title: Metal Gear Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Metal Gear Wiki!
items.desc: Welcome to the Metal Gear Wiki, your resource for all things Metal Gear! The Metal Gear Wiki is the ultimate resource of knowledge for the Metal Gear video game franchise. In addition to all canonical and non-canonical games, the wiki also covers remakes, updates, Entertainment, and even the people who develop the games.

items.name: MS Paint Adventures Wiki
items.title: MS Paint Adventures Wiki
items.headline: MS Paint Adventures Wiki
items.desc: MS Paint Adventures Wiki is a community site by and for fans of MS Paint Adventures, the website that is home to several web comics by the Godly-lipped Andrew Hussie. Covering Jailbreak, Bard Quest, Problem Sleuth, and Homestuck, MSPA wiki is dedicated to untangling all the weird plot stuff, all of it. Its scope also covers Hussie's other works, such as And It Don't Stop, Humanimals, et cetera.
